public interface FileSystem
extends com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.Capability

A representation of the model object 'File System'.

The following features are supported:

  • Available Space
  • Capacity
  • Mount Point
  • Type

See Also:
OsPackage.getFileSystem()
